text: Saw their Tik Tok video and decided to order murukku and papadam from them. First time ordering.  The murukku is fragrant and crispy. Perhaps they can make it less hard as elderly may have problems biting into the murukku. You can taste the spices used. Great snack while watching TV. Most importantly, there was no "stale oil" smell or taste.  They were very responsive to my questions and delivery was punctual.  Will recommend to my neighbours!
Surprised by their great taste and value for money.
So nice!! Love the taste and superb fast delivery
